<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.3">
<l>vāṉiḷa varacu vaikuntak kuṭṭaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">vācutē vaṉmatu raimaṉṉaṉ nanta</l>
<l>kōṉiḷa varacu kōvalar kuṭṭaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvin taṉkuḻal koṭūtiṉa pōtu</l>
<l>vāṉiḷam paṭiyar vantuvan tīṇṭi</l>
<l rend="indent">maṉamuru kimalark kaṇkaḷpa ṉippa</l>
<l>tēṉaḷa vuceṟi kūntala viḻac</l>
<l rend="indent">ceṉṉivērp paccevi cērttuniṉ ṟaṉarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When Govinda–</l>
<l rend="indent">the prince of heaven, the darling of Vaikuntha,</l>
<l rend="indent">Vāsudeva, king of Mathūrā,</l>
<l rend="indent">Prince of king Nanda, darling of the herders–</l>
<l>Played [his] flute,</l>
<l>Heavenly young ladies came and gathered,</l>
<l rend="indent">[their] hearts melting,</l> 
<l rend="indent">[their] flower[-like] eyeswelling with tears,</l>
<l rend="indent">[their] thick, fragrant tresses becoming loose,</l>
<l>[and] stood, ears afixed [to the sound], as [their] foreheads perspired.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
